org.dockbox.selene.core.inventory.pane

Interface StaticPane

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Pane
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SpongeStaticPane

    public interface StaticPane
extends Pane
    Represents a static (non-changing) pane, which can be updated without closing the pane.

      • update

        void update(InventoryLayout layout)
        Updates the pane. This will update the pane even if it is open to a player. This will not close the pane and open the updated version, and instead cleans and replaces the items currently displayed by the pane.
        Parameters:
        layout - The new layout to display.
